article_title: Nine Things You Won't Believe Obama Did In His Buzzfeed Video
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

President Obama is starring in a Buzzfeed video this week, using the opportunity to participate in the internet meme culture and to promote Obamacare.

SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

Here are 9 things that he did:

1. Smiled at himself in the mirror

2. Practiced shilling for Obamacare

3. Stuck out his tongue

4. Practiced looking cool

5. Used a selfie stick

6. Joined the “Thanks Obama” meme

7. Nailed it

8. Drew a picture of Michelle Obama

9. “Yolo man!”
